Title
EPM Agent and SSL TLS Inspection
Question
Does the EPM Agent Support SSL/TLS inspection or man-in-the-middle inspection?
Answer
No, the EPM agent does not support man-in-the-middle TLS inspection of web traffic

In order to validate if SSL Inspection is in-place, there's a few options depending upon your platform (be sure to use a URL that is applicable to region as outlined here - (https://docs.cyberark.com/epm/latest/en/content/installation/network-setup.htm?Highlight=firewall#ServiceURLsforaspecificregion)

Windows
Use a simple script (example attached to this KB) which will prompt you for parameters for comparison.
Be sure to supply the full URL (ex: https://agents-na.epm.cyberark.com)
