Network setup
This topic lists the EPM service URLs for EPM agents on all platforms.

This is relevant for organizations that implement outbound traffic rules.

Overview
To use the CyberArk EPM SaaS solution, endpoints where EPM agents are installed must have network access to different service URLs.

Use the URLs list below to configure your network components, such as firewall, WAF and proxy, to make sure endpoints with EPM agents have access to these URLs.

In addition, make sure that third-party application installed on the endpoints do not block communication with EPM SaaS.

Service URLs
If your organization uses SSL inspection, you must configure it to exclude the EPM service URLs listed in the following table.

This ensures communication between EPM agents and the SaaS service.

