Tenant URL

The main access point to the EPM service management console.

Open the tenant URL that is specific to your region, as listed in Service URLs for a specific region.

You can configure access to all EPM tenants URLs with *.epm.cyberark.com, instead of using the specific URL for your region.

Open port 443 HTTPS.

S3 URL

The main access point to EPM service downloadable content, such as agents installers, packages, etc.

Open the S3 URL that is specific to your region, as listed in Service URLs for a specific region.

Open port 443 HTTPS.

URL for endpoint-service communication

The main access point for agent communication to the CyberArk EPM service.

Open the service-endpoint communication URL that is specific to your region, as listed in Service URLs for a specific region.

Open port 443 TLS over TCP.

